    <item>
      <title>日本加密货币审查或为降低税收、推出专用 ETF 提供机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/japan-crypto-review-may-open-door-to-lower-taxes-dedicated-etfs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本即将开始审查该国的加密货币规则，这可能降低数字资产的税收，并可能为推出投资代币的国内基金铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/japan-crypto-review-may-open-door-to-lower-taxes-dedicated-etfs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 09:03:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
